- Install/upgrade guide: [README.md](https://github.com/${REPO}/blob/${TAG}/README.md)
- Hosting/TLS (Caddy + DuckDNS): [README_HOST.md](https://github.com/${REPO}/blob/${TAG}/README_HOST.md)

⚡ Quick Install:

```bash
gh release download ${TAG} --repo ${REPO} --pattern quick.sh --output quick.sh --clobber
chmod +x quick.sh
bash quick.sh install --repo ${REPO} --tag ${TAG}
```

🔄 Quick Upgrade:

```bash
gh release download ${TAG} --repo ${REPO} --pattern quick.sh --output quick.sh --clobber
chmod +x quick.sh
bash quick.sh upgrade --repo ${REPO} --tag ${TAG}
```

`--tag` is optional in `quick.sh` (defaults to latest), and version-style tags accept either `vX.Y.Z` or `X.Y.Z`.

Exact URL to paste into Stremio after success:

```text
$PUBLIC_BASE_URL/manifest.json
```

