## ✅ Minimal verification checklist

After install or upgrade, verify in this order:

- [ ] `sudo systemctl is-active stremio-addarr` returns `active`
- [ ] `curl -fsS http://127.0.0.1:7010/manifest.json >/dev/null` succeeds
- [ ] `curl -fI $PUBLIC_BASE_URL/manifest.json` returns `200`
- [ ] `PUBLIC_BASE_URL` exactly matches the Caddy hostname (`https://YOUR_HOSTNAME`)
- [ ] Stremio installs from `$PUBLIC_BASE_URL/manifest.json`
